@startuml State - Spots

skinparam stateFontSize 13
skinparam stateArrowFontSize 11
skinparam roundcorner 8

[*] --> AVAILABLE : seeded on system init

AVAILABLE --> LOCKED    : Reservation created\n(PENDING_PAYMENT)
LOCKED    --> AVAILABLE : Payment failed/expired\nor reservation cancelled
LOCKED    --> OCCUPIED  : Driver checks in\n(session ACTIVE)
OCCUPIED  --> AVAILABLE : Driver checks out\n(session COMPLETED)

@enduml
